<div class="tab-content" style="margin-right: 100px;"> 
  <style>
    li { line-height: 28px; }
  </style>
  <div class="eight columns">
    <ol>
      <li>To view streaming videos please ensure that you have the Quicktime Video plugin installed.  <a target="_blank" href="https://www.apple.com/quicktime/">Get Quicktime</a></li>
      <li>We recommend using <a href="https://www.google.com/intl/en/chrome/browser/" target="_blank">Google Chrome</a> or <a href=" https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/" target="_blank">Mozilla Firefox</a> to ensure compatibility. Currently Safari and Internet Explorer are not as reliable at playing streaming videos.</li>
      <li>Currently our streaming video server does not work with mobile devices. We are currently developing a better streaming solution that will allow you to stream to your smartphones and tablets soon.</li>
      <li>If students are having issues with streaming videos they can always use a computer in one of the labs on campus.</li>
      <li>A wired Ethernet connection is always recommend as it more reliable and faster than wifi.</li>
      <li>The Quicktime plugin for Windows does not allow for fullscreen video.</li>
      <li>If you are viewing videos from off campus we recommend you have at least a 2-3 megabit internet connection speed to ensure reliable viewing.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
  <div class="four columns">
    <h4>Click to Play Test Video</h4>
    <div style="border: 1px solid #E8E9E8; width: 190px; height: 260px;">
      <object classid="clsid:02BF25D5-8C17-4B23-BC80-D3488ABDDC6B" codebase="http://www.apple.com/qtactivex/qtplugin.cab" height="260" width="190">
        <param name="src" value="<%= URI.join(root_url, '/assets/QuickTime-sample.mov') %>">
        <param name="autoplay" value="false">
        <param name="target" value="myself">
        <param name="controller" value="true">
        <param name="href" value="<%= URI.join(root_url, '/assets/QuickTime-sample.mov') %>">
        <param name="type" value="video/quicktime" height="260" width="190">

        <embed src="<%= URI.join(root_url, '/assets/QuickTime-sample.mov') %>" height="260" width="190" autoplay="false" type="video/quicktime" pluginspage="http://www.apple.com/quicktime/download/" controller="true" href="<%= URI.join(root_url, '/assets/QuickTime-sample.mov') %>" target="myself"></embed>
      </object>
    </div>
    <p> If you are able to view this video quicktime is installed</p>
  </div>
</div>
